{
  "stem": "3040.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Besides that, we have attached ourself-- attached ourselves to an organization that is called Beit Halochem which is the House of the Warriors.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is the translation of Beit Halochem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is an organization to rehabilitate Jewish soldiers who were wounded or in any way are handicapped, you know, in the Israeli wars.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the-- the purpose of that organization, Beit Halochem, is to help rehabilitate these-- these soldiers and bring them back to become regular, productive citizens, if possible.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Some of them will never be, because they are-- they lost some limbs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Some lost their eyesight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But they are all being helped and rehabilitated in these facilities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In fact, we were in Israel three weeks ago, and we visited a new facility in Jerusalem of Beit Halochem.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they showed us the wonders that they do there for-- to rehabilitate the-- the-- the invalids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Besides-- well, besides that, we are still a friendship organization, and we do have get-togethers on certain occasions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Like, we organize Hanukkah parties.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We organize Yom Ha'atzmaut parties.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This is when Israel celebrates the independence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we get together-- in fact, next Sunday, we have a Yom Ha'atzmaut party.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's delayed now, because a lot of people were in Israel three weeks ago, and we have celebrated the Yom Ha'atzmaut in Israel this time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we have a lot of our-- our society is very diversified.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's very-- it's not only diversified, it is being acknowledged among-- in the survivor community.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, personally, also work with Benjamin Meed, who is the chairman of the-- of the WAGRO-- this is the Warsaw ghetto uprising organization-- and also the Together Federation of Jewish-- of Jewish Survivors.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And occasionally, I go to meetings that he has, and he calls, or he sends me notices and invitations.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
